data.description: This 4 bedroom 2 1/2 bath home completely updated with hardwood floors, tiled bathroom and kitchen floors, solid surface kitchen countertop along with tiled backsplash, stainless steel appliances, newer furnace and electrical panel, 2 paneled interior doors, vinyl siding, roof, gutters with leaf guards, all redone 4 years ago. Take your morning coffee on the attached deck directly off the kitchen. Enjoy cookouts on the 20X20 stamped concrete patio looking out the spacious backyard. The oversized 2 stall garage will come in handy, storing the outside lawn equipment.    Ask About 100% M.B.G. Excellent Condition
